      <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-black text-white md:text-5xl">常见问题先放出来，减少来回解释</h2>
      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2">
        {faq.map(([q, a]) => (
          <div class="rounded-[1.5rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/[.045] p-6">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white">{q}</h3>
            <p class="mt-3 leading-7 text-slate-400">{a}</p>
          </div>
